---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Documentation - Backlog Chef" description="Complete documentation for Backlog Chef - Transform meetings into high-quality Product Backlogs">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900">Documentation</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12">
        Everything you need to know about Backlog Chef and how it transforms your Scrum meetings into high-quality backlogs.
      </p>

      <!-- Vision -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          An intelligent system that transforms Scrum meetings into structured, high-quality Product Backlog Items
          with built-in quality assurance, context enrichment, and stakeholder intelligence.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- How It Works -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">1. Meeting Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">
              Connect your meeting transcription tool (Fireflies) to automatically capture your refinement meetings,
              sprint planning sessions, and backlog discussions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">2. AI-Powered Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">
              Our AI engine (powered by Claude) analyzes the transcript to extract Product Backlog Items,
              acceptance criteria, questions, and decisions with confidence scoring.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">3. Context Enrichment</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">
              Automatically enriches PBIs with historical context, similar past work, risk detection,
              and stakeholder routing using your existing tools (Jira, Azure DevOps, Confluence).
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">4. Quality Assurance</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">
              Each PBI is checked against Definition of Ready criteria, flagged for risks and conflicts,
              and scored for completeness before entering your sprint.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">5. Output to Your Tools</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">
              Export structured PBIs directly to your work tracking system or knowledge base
              (Azure DevOps, Jira, Obsidian, Confluence).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Core Features -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">10 Quality Tools</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">1. Context & Historical Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Learn from past work. Shows similar PBIs, what went wrong/right, estimates vs actuals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">2. Smart Examples & Templates</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Suggests proven structures based on PBI type (user story, technical improvement, bug fix).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">3. Proactive Risk Detection</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Flags complexity markers, dependencies, scope creep, affected systems automatically.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">4. Consistency Checking</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Detects terminology conflicts, contradictions, strategic alignment issues.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">5. Collaborative Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Routes questions to right stakeholders, flags required approvals, finds documentation gaps.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">6. Estimation Support</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Compares to similar work, analyzes complexity factors, suggests splits for large items.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">7. Definition of Ready Coach</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Objective assessment against checklist, categorizes gaps (blocking/warning/suggestion).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">8. Proposal Generation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Don't just ask questions - suggest answers! Proposes AC, test scenarios, technical approaches.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">9. Visual & Interactive Aids</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Finds related mockups, generates flow diagrams, creates impact maps.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">10. Production Feedback Loop</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm">Tracks actual vs estimated, learns from bugs and adoption, improves over time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Tech Stack -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">Technology Stack</h2>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">MVP (CLI)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Language:</strong> TypeScript/Node.js</li>
            <li><strong>AI Engine:</strong> Anthropic Claude API</li>
            <li><strong>Integration:</strong> Model Context Protocol (MCP) for data access</li>
            <li><strong>Storage:</strong> Local JSON</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">V1 (Web App)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Next.js, shadcn/ui, Vercel</li>
            <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, PostgreSQL, Redis</li>
            <li><strong>Real-time:</strong> WebSockets</li>
            <li><strong>Infrastructure:</strong> Vercel + Railway</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Integrations -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">Integrations</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Meeting Transcription</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">Fireflies.ai - Automatic meeting capture and transcription</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Work Tracking</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">Azure DevOps, Jira - Direct PBI creation and updates</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Knowledge Base</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">Confluence, Obsidian - Documentation and context enrichment</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">MCP Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700">Model Context Protocol for standardized external data access</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Roadmap -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">Roadmap</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-green-900">MVP (1-3 months)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>CLI interface for basic usage</li>
              <li>Meeting transcript extraction</li>
              <li>PBI generation with confidence scoring</li>
              <li>Azure DevOps output adapter</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 border-l-4 border-slate-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">V1 (3-6 months)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Web UI for team collaboration</li>
              <li>Real-time meeting features</li>
              <li>Multi-screen stakeholder views</li>
              <li>Advanced quality checks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-purple-900">V2 (6-12 months)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Platform with marketplace</li>
              <li>Custom integrations</li>
              <li>Enterprise features (SSO, on-prem)</li>
              <li>Advanced analytics and insights</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Getting Started -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 border-b-2 border-slate-700 pb-2">Getting Started</h2>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to transform your backlog process?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6">
            Join our beta program to get early access and help shape the future of Backlog Chef.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/#pricing" class="bg-white text-slate-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition text-center">
              View Pricing
            </a>
            <a href="/#contact" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition text-center">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
